## Basic Operations


```js
// Input
console.log(30 + 3.5)
console.log(2022 - 1969)
console.log(65 / 240)
console.log(0.2708 * 100)

/*output */

33.5
53
0.2708333333333333
27.08
```


## Mathematical Assignments

```js 
let levelUp = 10;
let powerLevel = 9001;
let multiplyMe = 32;
let quarterMe = 1152;

// Use the mathematical assignments in the space below:

levelUp += 5;
powerLevel -= 5;
multiplyMe *= 5;
quarterMe /= 5;

// The value of levelUp: 15
// The value of powerLevel: 8996
// The value of multiplyMe: 160
// The value of quarterMe: 230.4

```
